resolution gave gorbachev absolutely unlimited powers and a 
lawmaker who did not identify himself told the legislature it would 
make the president into a monarch 
but the legislature rejected a series of amendments designed to 
limit the presidents new powers 
ryzhkov the prime minister later told reporters there was no 
