consumer goods also set off a wave of panic buying 
when ryzhkovs reworked plan was submitted to lawmakers earlier 
this month it was criticized as little different than the 
original 
a radical plan drawn up by economist stanislav shatalin also was 
submitted to parliament this month it proposes a 500day 
transition that includes sovereignty for the 15 soviet republics 
