far higher than in the initial announcements an ongoing veterans 
administration study and a european study published in science 
magazine have failed to confirm the fischl studys results the 
newspaper said 
the newspaper said ms fischl claimed that the study was a 
doubleblind meaning neither the patients nor those giving the 
drug knew who was receiving azt but researchers have now 
