governmentbacked program in trouble 
the federal deposit insurance corp and the federal housing 
administration lost money in 1988 and 1989 and seem destined to 
lose again this year about half of farm loans by the farmers home 
administration are in default 
theres a lot more federally backed debt than that as you might 
surmise but much of it will never appear in the official budget 
deficit figures because the government simply shoved them away 
they are off budget 
