4753 million australian dollars or about 3964 million 
the merged company would take complete control of the telfer 
gold mine in western australias pilbara region 
newmont is offering one ordinary share for every two bhp gold 
shares the offer is contingent upon 51 per cent acceptance and 
newmont shareholders approving an increase in authorized capital 
the bhp co ltd currently holds 56 percent of bhp gold but its 
effective stake in the merged entity would total 23 percent 
while bhp is yet to announce its intentions under the merger 
proposal directors are expected to agree to the gold division 
being subsumed just three years after its listing 
