spain and new york city 
in reality greco was an investigator working for american 
express the journal said greco also had an arrest record in the 
united states and italy going back to 1962 and had been convicted 
on charges including theft conspiracy and handling stolen goods 
the newspaper said 
safras investigators also discovered the greco had a link at 
american express susan cantor now a senior vice president at 
american express bank and before that an employee in the american 
express public relations office working under harry freeman the 
journal said 
the journal said freeman had been a willing ear when 
american express bank officials began voicing their concerns about 
safra freeman had a penchant for unorthodox projects the 
newspaper said 
freeman was convinced that safra wanted to destroy american 
express bank and began collecting rumors about him the journal 
said 
the newspaper said freeman initially used ms cantor a former 
